[32m│[0m ## Summary                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### detailed_summary                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Successfully exploited an **IDOR (Insecure Direct Object Reference)          [32m│[0m
